              Well, my spotted cow clone didn't go as well as I'd hoped.  Through a combination of undershooting my efficiency a tad and over estimating my boil off, I ended up with 3 gallons of 1.038 instead of 2.5 gallons of 1.048.  Guess this one is going to be a session beer.<br /><br />Out of curiosity, there was lots of stuff in suspension for my hydrometer sample.  How does that impact the reading?

              

              
              
